en=\"true\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M328 256c0 39.8-32.2 72-72 72s-72-32.2-72-72 32.2-72 72-72 72 32.2 72 72zm104-72c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72zm-352 0c-39.8 0-72 32.2-72 72s32.2 72 72 72 72-32.2 72-72-32.2-72-72-72z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/button\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003cpre style=\"counter-reset: codeblock;\" class=\"tw-block tw-m-0 tw-p-0\"\u003e\u003ccode \n    id=\"codeblock-id-44\" \n    class=\"\n      chroma \n      !tw-block \n      tw-p-0\n      tw-m-0\n      tw-transition-[max-height] \n      tw-duration-500 \n      tw-ease-in-out \n      group-[.is-closed]:!tw-max-h-0 \n      group-[.is-wrap]:tw-text-wrap\n      tw-overflow-y-hidden\n      tw-overflow-x-auto\n      tw-scrollbar-thin\n      \"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"line\"\u003e\u003cspan class=\"cl\"\u003e[demo_wp_query]\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e👉 The query will be displayed when visiting \u003ccode\u003ehttp://localhost/\u0026lt;page-title\u0026gt;\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" href=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/demo_page.png\" title=\"demo page\" data-thumbnail=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/demo_page.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003eDemo page displaying WP_Query output\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003edemo page\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg  loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/demo_page.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/demo_page_hu_14b76e459957e279.webp 800w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/demo_page_hu_6224f037d0e1ce02.webp 1200w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/demo_page_hu_a78ec0fc7bf5394c.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"demo page\" height=\"895\" width=\"1306\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003eDemo page displaying WP_Query output\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ch2 id=\"analysis\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#analysis\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e45 Analysis\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003ewpdb\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eCore PHP class used by WordPress to directly interact with MySQL.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAllows developers to \u003cstrong\u003ewrite and execute raw SQL queries\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eWP_Query\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eAn abstraction layer that retrieves post data from the database \u003cstrong\u003ewithout writing raw SQL\u003c/strong\u003e.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eDevelopers simply pass an array of parameters (args), and WordPress automatically builds the appropriate SQL.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eRelationship\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cul\u003e\n\u003cli\u003e\u003ccode\u003eWP_Query\u003c/code\u003e doesn’t directly query MySQL.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003cli\u003eInstead, it builds SQL based on the arguments, applies \u003cstrong\u003evalidation/sanitization\u003c/strong\u003e, and then calls \u003ccode\u003e$wpdb\u003c/code\u003e to execute it.\u003c/li\u003e\n\u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"patch-diff\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#patch-diff\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e45.1 Patch Diff\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eWordPress is an \u003cstrong\u003eopen-source\u003c/strong\u003e project with a public GitHub repository, meaning all patches are committed openly.\nTo analyze a vulnerability, we can simply review the related commit and observe the code changes.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe reference for \u003cstrong\u003eCVE-2022-21661\u003c/strong\u003e links to this \u003ca href=\"https://github.com/WordPress/wordpress-develop/commit/17efac8c8ec64555eff5cf51a3eff81e06317214\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"\u003ecommit\u003c/a\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003ca class=\"lightgallery\" href=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/patch_diff.png\" title=\"Patch Diff\" data-thumbnail=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/patch_diff.png\" data-sub-html=\"\u003ch2\u003ePatch diff between versions\u003c/h2\u003e\u003cp\u003ePatch Diff\u003c/p\u003e\"\u003e\u003cimg  loading=\"lazy\" src='/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/patch_diff.png' srcset=\"/2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/patch_diff_hu_c2fd4fd5f6523e81.webp 800w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/patch_diff_hu_3bbadfa784273ef4.webp 1200w, /2025-10-01-cve-2022-21661/patch_diff_hu_aaff74cf9da5518a.webp 1600w\"  alt=\"Patch Diff\" height=\"389\" width=\"830\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e\u003cfigcaption class=\"image-caption\"\u003ePatch diff between versions\u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe vulnerability was fixed in \u003cstrong\u003esrc/wp-includes/class-wp-tax-query.php\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eVulnerable Code\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n        tw-mx-2 \n        tw-flex\n        tw-flex-row\n        tw-flex-1\"\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @